> has accepted a designer position here at WebDevStudios! Jayvie has been building websites on WordPress since it was first released. He took an interest in web design and turned it into a passion. For years he has been working in a sales job during the day and freelancing on the side, but recently he quit his day job and dove into full-time freelancing. His stint with full-time freelancing is short lived and he will start working with us in the next few weeks!</p>\n<p>Jay will be the lead designer in our newly established small business department which will focus on creating well designed, affordable websites for small businesses and individuals. Jay&#8217;s experience in sales and knowledge of best WordPress design practices will allow him to excel at designing websites for a variety of different clients.</p>\n<p>Welcome to WebDev, Jay! We are excited to have you!</p>\n<p>Find out more about Jay on our <a title="Jayvie Canono" href="http://webdevstudios.com/team/jayvie-canono/">team page</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:90:"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/12/05/another-addition-to-the-wds-family-jayvie-canono/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"8";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:19:"Welcome Tom Carney!";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"d