g in the <a href="http://wpcandy.com/stream">live interactive chat</a>. Find out about upcoming episodes on <a href="http://www.facebook.com/WpLateNight">Facebook</a> or at <a href="http://wplatenight.com">WPLateNight.com</a> and listen in live on the <a href="http://wpcandy.com/stream">WP Candy livestream</a>.</p>\n<p><span style="line-height: 24px;">Missed out on the live recording? Tune in to the latest episode (or any past episode) on </span><a style="line-height: 24px;" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/wpcandydotcom/videos?view=0">YouTube</a><span style="line-height: 24px;">, </span><a style="line-height: 24px;" href="http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/wp-late-night/id496147707">iTunes</a><span style="line-height: 24px;">, or download the </span><a style="line-height: 24px;" href="http://wpcandy.com/category/broadcasts/wp-late-night">MP3 file</a><span style="line-height: 24px;">.</span></p>\n<h3><strong>WP Late Night airs live every Wednesday at 8pm Eastern. <a href="http://wpcandy.com/stream">Tune in tonight!</a></strong></h3>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:75:"http://webdevstudios.com/2012/09/26/have-you-tuned-into-wp-late-night/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:40:"WordCamp Grand Rapids is just days away!";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0